snippet.title: 'Man in the Dark' GamePlay
snippet.description:
Man in the Dark is a dark-feeling third-person shooter, single-play game that realistically depicts the earth's apocalyptic feeling, set in a human race that has been turned into a place where zombies and monsters are rampant due to people's wrong choices.


#zombie #tps #shooter
